Here is the mapping for the metrics in the `get_sales_transaction_by_guid` response, comparing the **JSON field name**, the **English version**, and the **Russian version** used in the PlanFact UI:

### Graph & Progress Bar Metrics (Graphic Data)

| JSON Field | English Version | Russian Version (UI) | Description |
| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **`receipts_percentage`** | Received (%) | **Поступило (%)** | Percentage of money received vs. total deal value. |
| **`shipments_percentage`** | Shipped (%) | **Отгружено (%)** | Percentage of products shipped vs. total deal value. |
| **`client_debt`** | Client Debt | **Клиент должен** | Total deal value minus money received. |
| **`remaining_shipment`** | Remaining to Ship | **Осталось отгрузить** | Total deal value minus products already shipped. |

---

### Profitability & Financial Header Metrics

| JSON Field | English Version | Russian Version (UI) | Description |
| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **`profitability`** | Profitability (%) | **Рентабельность** | Profit margin expressed as a percentage. |
| **`total_expenses_summa`** | Total Expenses | **Расходы** | Total money spent/allocated as expenses to the deal. |

---

### Total Reference Values

| JSON Field | English Version | Russian Version (UI) | Description |
| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **`total_products_summa`** | Total Deal Value | **Сумма сделки** | Total sum of all products/services in the deal. |
| **`total_receipts_summa`** | Total Received | **Всего поступило** | Absolute sum of money received. |
| **`total_shipment_summa`** | Total Shipped | **Всего отгружено** | Absolute sum of products delivered. |

 